title: Drone captures last moments of Lashkar terrorists killed in Pulwama encounter | Jammu and Kashmir
description: A drone camera of security forces has captured the last moments of three Lashkar-e-Taiba militants killed in an encounter yesterday in Pulwama district of south Kashmir. The footage shows three Lashkar militants positioning themselves outside a residential house to take on security personnel who had cornered them from all sides. All the three militants, which include a 9-day old teen recruit from Srinagar, were shot dead in a brief firefight. title: Jokowi dan Anies Tinjau Lokasi Formula E: Awal Juni Lihat Balapannya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV   - Presiden Joko Widodo bersama Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan telah meninjau lokasi Formula E, pada Senin (25/4/2202). ||||Pada kesempatan itu Presiden Jokowi menjawab sejumlah pertanyaan awak media terkait persiapan pelaksanaan Formula E. ||||"Saya ingin melihat persiapan formula E seperti apa di lapangan. Kita lihat untuk trek balapannya sudah siap tinggal dikejar pemasangan paddock, grandstand, pagar, masih ada waktu abis lebaran. Kita harapkan awal Juni melihat balapannya,"ucap Jokowi. ||||Baca Juga Didampingi Anies, Jokowi Tinjau Pembangunan Sirkuit Formula E di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283234/didampingi-anies-jokowi-tinjau-pembangunan-sirkuit-formula-e||||Kemudian Anies pun menjelaskan untuk trek balapan sudah siap 100 persen. ||||"Izin pak presiden, kalau untuk trek 100 persen, dalam proses pembangunan paddock, grandstand, dan pagar, nanti di pagar beton ada pagar untuk pelindung. Itu semua lagi dikerjakan, fasilitas tamu-tamu, Secara umu treknya sudah 100 persen,"jelas Anies pada media.||||Lebih lanjut Formula E akan digelar di Ancol, Jakarta Utara pada Juni mendatang tepatnya pada pada 4 Juni 2022.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283247/jokowi-dan-anies-tinjau-lokasi-formula-e-awal-juni-lihat-balapannya

VERIVERY SERIES ‚ÄòO‚Äô [ROUND 3 : WHOLE]|From the ‚ÄòFACE it‚Äô series delving into the concept of ‚Äòfacing the many selves co-existing in oneself‚Äô to the ‚ÄòSERIES ‚ÄòO‚Äô‚Äô series and its exploration of the ‚Äòdarkness within‚Äô that all dread facing, yet must, VERIVERY has developed a stable foundation for its world-building over its releases. The world-building now reaches its spectacular height through VERIVERY‚Äôs first full album [ROUND 3 : WHOLE].|Hello Darkness, Learning How to Co-exist with It|Through the story strewn across SERIES ‚ÄòO‚Äô VERIVERY had found O, a space of darkness, at a party that they were invited to by mysterious figures, eventually facing what was at its core. In the end, ‚Äòdarkness‚Äô is a necessity that one must learn to co-exist with in order to live on. However, the interpretation of this notion, as well as the means to do so, must be reached individually.|‚ÄòIt‚Äôs Coming, the Perfect Time‚Äô ‚Äì Finally, the Endgame!|The endgame is the point when conflicts come to a close. The album cover depicts a circle reminiscent of fight rings to clearly showcase the album‚Äôs main message, while the antique elevator set introduces an air of mystery to the atmosphere. As well, the concept films connecting the new story to previous installments of the series make effective use of ambience in order to create suspense as if one was watching a horror film. title: Marcon defeats far-right rival Le Pen; Vows to unite France after bagging 2nd term
description: French President Emmanuel Macron defeated far-right rival Marine Le Pen by a comfortable margin. Macron secured a second term, heading off what would have been a political earthquake. Cheers of joy erupted as results appeared on a screen at the Champ de Mars park at the foot of the Eiffel tower. Supporters waved French & EU flags - people hugged each other, danced and chanted 'Macron!'. Le Pen, who at one stage trailed Macron by a few points in opinion polls, quickly admitted defeat. However, Le Pen vowed to keep up the fight, with parliamentary elections looming in June. Watch the full video for more.|#EmmanuelMacron #MarineLePen #France #Macron

description: KARAWANG, KOMPAS.TV - Uji coba ganjil genap tol telah dilakukan pada pukul 11.00 WIB hari ini, Senin 25 April 2022.||||Dimulai dari gerbang Tol Cikampek Utama kilometer 47.||||Baca Juga Uji Coba Ganjil Genap Tol Cikampek, Jasa Marga Siagakan Petugas hingga Pemasangan Rambu di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282984/uji-coba-ganjil-genap-tol-cikampek-jasa-marga-siagakan-petugas-hingga-pemasangan-rambu||||Uji coba ganjil genap dilakukan selama tiga hari, dengan tujuan untuk mengurai kemacetan selama arus mudik lebaran 2022.||||Data dari Kementerian Perhubungan, bakal ada 85 juta pemudik, tahun ini dengan 47 persennya, yakni sekitar 40 juta orang menggunakan jalur darat.||||Baca Juga Warga Mulai PadatI Hotel Jelang Puncak Mudik Tiba, Pengusaha Hotel Mulai Dapat Angin Segar di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283123/warga-mulai-padati-hotel-jelang-puncak-mudik-tiba-pengusaha-hotel-mulai-dapat-angin-segar||||Karena itu, uji coba aturan ganjil genap diberlakukan. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283126/hari-pertama-uji-coba-ganjil-genap-di-tol-cikampek-antisipasi-macet-selama-arus-mudik-lebaran-2022

title: Ax-1 Mission | Undocking

After performing a series of burns to move away from the space station, Dragon will conduct multiple orbit-lowering maneuvers, jettison its trunk, and re-enter Earth‚Äôs atmosphere before landing off the coast of Florida 16 hours later at approximately 1:06 p.m. ET on Monday, April 25.|Live webcast coverage will begin about fifteen minutes prior to undocking and resume about one hour before prior to splashdown.

title: WW2 Guns Still Used in Today's Ukraine war
description: For centuries wars are being fought with contemporary weapons and in some instances with  future or prototype ones. However some old weapons, older than their current users, are being utilized. The Ukraine war has shown that some very old designs can still be used. Machine guns from a century ago, bolt action rifles older than that, submachine guns designed for WW2, anti-tank rifles as relics of the same conflict are being used, in big numbers or some rare occasions.|ÔªøEach of these weapons   tell  us a story and serve as a testament of durability and the overall change and shift in the military doctrine as well as the consequences of the current situation. Not only that but those weapons, very crude and old, are serving on par with the latest designs, making the situation even more peculiar.|ÔªøMost of those weapons have survived the harsh conditions of the biggest conflict in human history, years of storage and later wars beyond that. title: Veroordeelde OPLICHTSTER Adriana J. KEIHARD AANGEPAKT! | Undercover in Nederland
description: Undercover in Nederland is te zien bij SBS6. |Bekijk alle afleveringen op KIJK.nl: https://bit.ly/3ybdUEB|ABONNEER op SBS6 voor meer video's: http://bit.ly/2qiTx8c|VOLG SBS6 op social media! |Facebook | SBS6|TikTok | SBS6nl|Instagram | SBS6NL|OVER Undercover in Nederland...|Het is inmiddels een vertrouwd straatbeeld: pakketbezorgers en medewerkers van bezorgdiensten zoals Thuisbezorgd, staan dagelijks voor de deur. Overvallers weten dat ook en maken daar op een vreselijke manier misbruik van. De afgelopen tijd kwam het ene na het andere nieuwsbericht over deze zorgwekkende trend naar buiten. Bekende en onbekende Nederlanders worden op verschrikkelijke wijze overvallen in hun eigen huis. In deze uitzending van Undercover in Nederland duiken Alberto Stegeman en zijn team in de schimmige wereld van de handel in uniformen, die door criminelen worden gebruikt voor brute overvallen en inbraken. Gewapend met verborgen camera's starten zij een onderzoek naar deze dubieuze handel. Het gaat om kleding van bezorgdiensten, maar ook politiekleding wordt online aangeboden. Er zijn meerdere confrontaties met de aanbieders en als een louche dealer politiekleding aanbiedt en Alberto hem wil confronteren, is ook de politie zelf niet ver uit de buurt.

description: En este v√≠deo te voy a ense√±ar 8 consejos para mejorar la circulaci√≥n de las piernas y evitar as√≠ la aparici√≥n de varices.|0:00 INTRO|0:23 ¬øC√ìMO FUNCIONA EL SISTEMA CIRCULATORIO?|Nuestro coraz√≥n bombea la sangre arterial, es decir sangre rica en ox√≠geno a todas las partes del cuerpo, incluido las zonas m√°s lejanas como los dedos de los pies.|Una vez que la sangre ha transportado el ox√≠geno a todo el cuerpo, se convierte en sangre venosa. No existe ning√∫n coraz√≥n en las piernas que propulse la sangre, y adem√°s tenemos la fuerza de la gravedad que dificulta a√∫n m√°s el retorno venoso. Hay varios mecanismos que favorecen este retorno.|1:06 ¬øC√ìMO SE PRODUCE EL RETORNO VENOSO?|En primer lugar la planta del pie, es como una esponja, al poner peso sobre el pie o mover los dedos de los pies conseguimos que esa red de venas se vac√≠e, como si estuvi√©ramos apretando una esponja.|Adem√°s la contracci√≥n muscular, espec√≠ficamente la contracci√≥n del gemelo, al que denominamos segundo coraz√≥n, es el mecanismo estrella a la hora de bombear la sangre de las piernas hasta el torso.|El diafragma en la respiraci√≥n produce un efecto de vac√≠o en el abdomen, y el propio coraz√≥n tiene un efecto de aspiraci√≥n que favorece el retorno aunque bien mucho menos importante que cuando propulsa la sangre venosa.|Adem√°s de todo esto, las venas tienen un sistema de v√°lvulas que permite el movimiento de la sangre venosa en una sola direcci√≥n, como cuando se infla un flotador en la playa, la sangre venosa sube cerr√°ndose la v√°lvula detr√°s impidiendo que la sangre vuelva a bajar.|4:14 ACTIVIDAD DEPORTIVA|El primer consejo es llevar a cabo actividad f√≠sica de forma regular. Pero, no cualquier actividad f√≠sica, la OMS recomienda completar al menos 150 minutos de actividad de moderada a vigorosa a la semana, para mantener una buena salud mental y cardiovascular.|Si cuando realizas una actividad deportiva, eres capaz de mantener una conversaci√≥n tranquilamente, est√°s llevando a cabo una actividad de intensidad baja.|Si por el contrario cuando haces deporte puedes mantener una conversaci√≥n pero notas que te falta el aire, entonces est√°s llevando a cabo una actividad de intensidad moderada.|Si por √∫ltimo no puedes mantener una conversaci√≥n cuando llevas a cabo tu actividad deportiva se trata, sin lugar a dudas de una actividad vigorosa.|6:00 EVITAR EL SEDENTARISMO|Si te falta tiempo y no puedes hacer deporte durante la semana, intenta moverte todo lo posible, evita permanecer largos periodos de tiempo sentado o inm√≥vil. Ejercicios como estos que te propongo aqu√≠ te ayudar√°n a mantenerte activo y mejorar la circulaci√≥n incluso si pasas todo el d√≠a sentado. Estos otros ejercicios te ayudar√°n si trabajas de pie durante todo el d√≠a.|6:27 DEJAR LAS SUSTANCIAS TOXICAS|No consumir sustancias toxicas como el tabaco y el alcohol tiene un impacto muy beneficioso para tu circulaci√≥n y tu sistema cardiovascular, esto seguramente ya lo sab√≠as, as√≠ que espero que empieces a tomarte las cosas enserio y reduzcas el consumo de estas sustancias.|6:46 CUIDAR LA DIETA|Cuidar la dieta es el siguiente de los pasos, yo no soy nutricionista pero no es necesario serlo, usa tu sentido com√∫n a la hora de preparar tus comidas. No abuses de alimentos superprocesados, evita la sal y el az√∫car en cantidades excesivas. Hoy en d√≠a gracias al nutriscore lo tenemos mas f√°cil a la hora de elegir alimentos. Elige siempre aquellos que est√©n entre la A y la C y huye de los que se encuentren por detr√°s de la C.|7:16 MEDIAS DE COMPRESI√ìN|El uso de medias de compresi√≥n puede ser una buena idea siempre que te lo recomiende tu m√©dico. Deben usarse de manera puntual, cuando tengas que hacer frente a una larga jornada, o sepas que vas a estar de pie sin moverte durante todo el d√≠a.|8:00 BA√ëOS DE CONTRASTE|Los ba√±os de contraste, alternando agua fr√≠a y caliente puede ayudar al retorno venoso despu√©s de un d√≠a dif√≠cil. El efecto del calor y el fr√≠o sobre las arterias y las venas es vasodilatador y vasoconstrictor provocando una especie de contracci√≥n en los vasos sangu√≠neos. |8:31 ROPA AJUSTADA SOBRE TODO EN GEMELO E INGLE|Evitar el uso de ropa ajustada, sobre todo en la zona de los gemelos y la ingle, y limitar el uso de talones puede ser tambi√©n √∫til. Al usar talones la planta del pie no se apoya correctamente y el gemelo no se activa muscularmente lo que disminuye el efecto de los mecanismos de retorno venoso que mencionamos al principio.|8:54 ELEVAR LOS PIES DE LA CAMA|Tambi√©n puedes elevar los pies de la cama unos cent√≠metros de esta manera las piernas permanecer√°n por encima del coraz√≥n durante la noche favoreciendo gracias a la gravedad el retorno venoso y el vaciado de las piernas. title: I'm ADDICTED to my Porsche Taycan 4S Cross Turismo! - 9000 Mile Full Review
description: Install Raid for Free¬†‚úÖ¬†IOS/ANDROID/PC: https://clcr.me/D6yFNL and get a special starter pack¬†üí•¬†Available only for the next 30 days|Welcome back to RBR guys & this is my own #Porsche Taycan Cross Turismo. Last time I drove it on the channel it was the German Press car Cross Turismo Turbo S that top gear had half destroyed off roading it. And what a car it was! The aggressive super wagon looks rivalled even the RS6, and the massive speed and practicality won us all over, so much so that I bought one and you guys viewed the video almost a million times.|As of today I‚Äôve done over 9000(!?) miles in my 4S, in mere months as my combustion cars lay gathering dust.|Why have I been so addicted to it? What makes it better than my other daily #supercars? What did I love and what did I hate? These are some off the questions I‚Äôll answer in todays review and report on living with my first #EV from Porsche, so let‚Äôs get to it and review my cross Turismo 4S!|So as a reminder - the two-tier Performance Battery Plus used in the Taycan Turbo S comes as standard in the CT, it‚Äôs just under 100kw size and it can charge from 20% to 80% in 20 minutes!|At home I use the CTEK Home Charger, as seen in the video:|https://www.ctek.com/uk/ev-charging/chargestorm¬Æ-connected-910-17028|The electric motors used are Permanent magnet synchronous electric motors, or PSM. These are always alive and give much higher output without overheating vs systems used in past Teslas. The 4S has a 600-amp pulse inverter which is our motor on the rear, and a 300 AMP inverter on the front too; and of course the 2 speed gearbox, 1st gear is mainly used in Sport or Sport Plus modes.|Technical Changes Vs  the standard Taycan include a more off road and yet more compliant suspension, using a three-chamber air set up giving a wide range of spring rates & heights. The rear is way larger, we have 47 mm more headroom and a boot with 40 litres more and the all important hatchback - I‚Äôll give you some storage tips on this.|The more important thing is perfoance however, here the 4S Cross Turismo has  490HP on the road and then overboost and Launch Control of 571. They say acceleration 0-60 is 4.1 seconds‚Ä¶ this is a bald faced lie! Wait to see the launch info here.|Having done 9000 miles, I‚Äôm gonna focus on my experience with this car as my first electric vehicle. That means telling you guys all the things I discovered, things I loved, things that really irritated me, and in general why I‚Äôm sold on the Taycan as a product.|As an example, PCM in Taycan crashes with black screens a lot, so I give you a Debug screen fix to help owners. I discover how Lift mode is really useful, how to clean the rear camera which was not obvious (neither way vent control inside) and find an amazing dynamic ambient light option!|The main point I wanna put across, is how I feel living with this versus something like an E 63 or the M5 - which is where I see this car fitting! title: India's payback for Beijing not allowing Indian students' return? Chinese tourist visas suspended
description: India has suspended tourist visas issued to Chinese nationals, global airlines body IATA told its member carriers on April 20. India has been raising with China the plight of approximately 22,000 Indian students enrolled in Chinese universities who are unable to go back for physical classes. However, the neighbouring country has till date refused to let them enter. These students had to leave their studies in China and come to India when the COVID-19 pandemic began in the beginning of 2020. description: PUTINS KRIEG: US-Minister Blinken und Austin in Kiew erwartet ‚Äì Beschuss auch √ºber Orthodoxe Ostern|Alle Aufrufe zu einer Feuerpause am orthodoxen Osterfest an diesem Sonntag fruchteten nicht. Russland setzte seine Angriffe gegen die Ukraine fort. "Zwei Kindern aus der Gemeinde Otscheretyne ist am Ostermorgen von den russischen Besatzern das Leben genommen worden", so teilte der Gouverneur der Region (Oblast) Donezk, Pawlo Kyrylenko, in seinem Telegram-Kanal mit. Die Angreifer zerst√∂rten demnach das Haus in dem ostukrainischen Ort, in dem die 14 und 5 Jahre alten M√§dchen gelebt h√§tten. F√ºr diese Verbrechen "wird es keine Vergebung geben - weder von Gott noch von den Menschen", so Kyrylenko.|Russlands Armee feuerte in der Nacht zum Sonntag laut Moskaus Verteidigungsministerium auf 423 Ziele in der Ukraine. Raketen und Artillerie h√§tten 26 Kommandoposten sowie fast 400 milit√§rische Stellungen sowie vier Waffen- und Munitionslager getroffen, sagte Ministeriumssprecher Igor Konaschenkow. Die Angaben beider Kriegsparteien konnten von unabh√§ngiger Seite nicht √ºberpr√ºft werden.|Die traditionell n√§chtlichen Ostermessen mussten wegen des Krieges fast in der ganzen Ukraine auf den Sonntagmorgen verschoben werden. Die Beh√∂rden bestanden auf der jede Nacht bis f√ºnf Uhr dauernden Ausgangssperre. Rund 70 Prozent der Ukrainer geh√∂ren einer der beiden orthodoxen Kirchen oder der mit Rom verbundenen griechisch-katholischen Kirche an und feiern Ostern nach dem alten Julianischen Kalender. Die Kirchenoberh√§upter verbreiteten in ihren Gottesdiensten in Kiew Zuversicht und Osterfreude - wie es dem h√∂chsten Feiertag der Auferstehung Christi entspricht.|Das schlimme Leid des Kriegs sprachen Geistliche dennoch in vielen Ostermessen an. Metropolit Epiphanius von der eigenst√§ndigen (autokephalen) orthodoxen Kirche der Ukraine hatte schon im Vorfeld Parallelen zwischen dem Schicksal des Landes und der Kreuzigung Jesu gezogen. Russland bezeichnete er auf Twitter als "wirkliches Reich des B√∂sen". Die Ostertage seien f√ºr Christen heilig; doch das russische Milit√§r zerst√∂re weiter ukrainische St√§dte und D√∂rfer und t√∂te unschuldige Menschen.|Durch einen russischen Raketenangriff auf die Schwarzmeermetropole Odessa seien am Samstag mehrere Zivilisten ums Leben gekommen oder verletzt worden, so Epiphanius. Seine Ostergl√ºckw√ºnsche verband er mit den Worten: "M√∂gen Ihre Herzen mit festem Vertrauen auf den Sieg des Guten und Wahren, auf den Sieg der Ukraine erf√ºllt sein."|Kiews griechisch-katholischer Gro√üerzbischof Swjatoslaw Schewtschuk sprach √§hnlich: vom "Feiertag des Sieges des Lebens √ºber den Tod, des Sieges der Wahrheit √ºber die Unwahrheit, des Sieges des Guten √ºber das B√∂se". Der Krieg dauere nun schon genau zwei Monate. Es gebe einen "neuen Siegesruf": "Wenn wir die Freude dar√ºber teilen wollen, dass wir unseren Feind aufgehalten haben, sagen wir: "Guten Tag, wir sind aus der Ukraine!" title: Can the global criminal network be destroyed? | DW Documentary
description: Organized crime can hold sway over political and economic institutions. Illegal business is growing more profitable every day. Can something be done to take down this global criminal network?|Corruption and drug trafficking are no longer just local problems. International groups working with terrorist organizations and politicians are ruthlessly spreading violence and endangering innocent lives. Complex infrastructures enable them to evade capture and punishment.  |Drug smuggling is a competitive global business. Drug smugglers transport their goods from Latin America to Europe. From international money laundering to transnational murder for hire, we see the devastation underground business leaves in its wake. Murders, explosions, and targeted attacks - they affect not only criminals, but also their families, witnesses, journalists, and other innocent victims. |According to FBI and Europol documents, every country on earth now has its own criminal groups and cartels. They are also gaining a stronger footing in Germany. Take drug trafficking, for example: Germany is a well-organized market and central transport hub for opiates along the Balkan route. South America directly serves the U.S. market. Anyone attempting to expose these groups is placing her or his life on the line.  |According figures from the World Bank, organized crime groups spend half of their annual two trillion dollar annual profits bribing politicians across the globe. Those operating with full cooperation from the authorities are behaving more like terror organizations: They use fear and terror, murder and manslaughter. But using the global financial system for money laundering is nothing new.  The state earns money through taxes and terror groups get rich in the process.|Drugs and money are not the only things being transported. Smuggling people has also become a lucrative business for organized crime, bringing in about $150 billion each year. |Could conditions like those in Russia develop elsewhere, where politicians, secret services and criminals share common interests? Could this even happen in once stable democracies like the USA or core European states? Is there a way out? Or are law enforcement agencies powerless to stop them?|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: 15 Heroes Spider-Man Could Team Up With Next
description: The friendly neighborhood webhead has an interesting future ahead of him in the MCU. After the heartbreaking conclusion to Spider-Man: No Way Home that left Peter Parker not only with his Aunt May gone, but also basically with his identity erased, it has set the stage for the young hero to be a little more independent in his next adventure. But as fun as it is watching solo Spider-Man movies, it‚Äôs also a blast seeing Peter Parker team up with other heroes! He‚Äôs so fun to watch when he has another Avenger to bounce off of and I think a team up movie could be a lot of fun in the future! But who would he work with best?|I think the logical choice would be Daredevil. The two have already interacted a little bit in the MCU, and having Spider-Man team up with the Man Without Fear would be an interesting way to further Peter‚Äôs personal journey. He‚Äôs used to fighting huge, world-ending threats now, so how would Peter function against a crime boss like Kingpin? He‚Äôd have to adopt a totally different set of skills! Or what about a new hero like Yelena? She could show Peter a grittier side of what it takes to be a hero in a street-level type of adventure! Or instead of street-level, would you have Peter go back to the cosmic side of things and team up with the Guardians of the Galaxy? There‚Äôs a lot of options!|So join me today as I break down all the different heroes Spidey could team up with in the future. title: PM Modi's first visit to J&K after Art 370 purge. He has this message for Kashmiri youth
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi assured Kashmiri youth on Sunday that he won't let them suffer like their parents and grandparents and will work towards making their life better and prosperous. PM Modi addressed a huge gathering in Jammu today and it was his first visit to J&K after his government stripped the erstwhile state of its special status and statehood. PM Modi also lauded the fact that all Indian laws are now applicable in Jammu and Kashmir and that all J&K residents are equal citizens of India. Watch the video for more.|#JammuKashmir #Jammu #Kashmir  #Article370 #NarendraModi #BJP #PMModi #Pakistan #India

title: Jammu man makes PM Modi's six-foot statue in record time; Gets praise from the Prime Minister
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi met a renowned sculptor from Jammu named Ravinder Jamwal  who made a 6-foot-tall statue of Prime Minister. PM Modi took the time out to meet the sculptor and laud him for the statue effort. PM Modi was in J&K for the first time since abrogation of article 370. PM Modi and J&K Lt governor Manoj Sinha posed for a picture with the sculptor and his wife. Watch this video for more.|#Jammu #PMModi #J&K #RavinderJamwal #ModiStatue #India #Viral #Trending #Video

title: Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel: Strengthening Connectivity, Boosting Tourism
description: Prime Minister inaugurated the Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel. The 8.45 Km long tunnel would reduce the road distance between Banihal and Qazigund by 16 km, and reduce journey time by around one and a half hour. It is a twin tube tunnel ‚Äì one for each direction of travel ‚Äì with the twin tubes being interconnected by a cross passage every 500m, for maintenance and emergency evacuation. The tunnel would help establish an all weather connection between Jammu and Kashmir, and bring the two regions closer.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! üîî||||Follow us to stay updated:||||‚ñ∫ Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||‚ñ∫ Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||‚ñ∫ Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||‚ñ∫ Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi

title: Ukrainians, Russians mark Orthodox Easter in time of war | DW News
description: Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskyy visited Kyiv's St. Sofia Cathedral to record an Easter message on the holiest day of the Orthodox Christian calendar. At makeshift prayer venues and churches around the country, Ukrainians prayed for those fighting on the front lines, and for those trapped in places like the besieged city of Mariupol. DW Correspondent Rebecca Ritters visited one village north east of Kyiv that was under Russian control until a few weeks ago. The community there came together to build a makeshift chapel after Russian soldiers destroyed their church.|Like Ukraine, Russia is also a predominantly Orthodox country. President Vladimir Putin attended an Easter mass early on Sunday in Moscow's Christ the Savior Cathedral. |The service was led by the head of the Russian Orthodox Church Patriach Kirill, who said he hoped the conflict in Ukraine would end quickly. Kirill has strongly backed the Kremlin's war in Ukraine. description: Hallo The Onsu..|Duh hari ini Ayah Ruben lagi kurang fit nih The Onsu, meriang gitu. title: Ketum IDI Temui Panglima TNI Andhika Perkasa, Bahas Soal Terawan?
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Ketua Umum Ikatan Dokter Indonesia (IDI) dan Jajaran Pengurus bertemu dengan Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa.||||Hal ini diunggah di kanal Youtube Jenderal TNI Andika Perkasa pada Minggu (24/4)||||Dalam kesempatan itu, Ketua Umum IDI Adib Hidayat memperkenalkan pengurus baru IDI Hasil Muktamar Aceh.||||Dalam kesempatan itu, Ketum IDI juga membahas megnenai keputusan pemberhentian tetap Terawan dari keanggotaan IDI.||||Adib menjelaskan basih memberi ruang kepada terawan untuk menjadi Anggota kembali.||||"Pemberhentian tetap itu tidak diartikan seumur hidup. Jadi masih ada upaya ruang kalau kami sampaikan masih ada ruang kalau beliau berkenan untuk menjadi anggota kembali kita akan kuatkan forum secara internal," ucap Adib.||||Tanggapi hal tersebut, Panglima TNI Andika Perkasa bertanya mengenai pengaruh keputusan pemberhentian Terawan dari IDI dan Izin prakteknya di RSPAD Gatot Subroto.||||"Apa yang berpengaruh terhadap izin praktek Dokter Terawan di RSPAD kalau keanggotaan beliau tidak lagi aktif tetapi sebagai dokter yang juga praktek di rumah sakit kami? Itu juga kita akan ikut aturan," tanya Andika.||||Video Editor: Faqih Fisabilillah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282954/ketum-idi-temui-panglima-tni-andhika-perkasa-bahas-soal-terawan

title: Kebijakan Presiden Larang Ekspor Minyak Disebut Tak Akan Turunkan Harga Minyak Goreng
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Hanya berselang tiga hari, setelah Dirjen Perdagangan Luar Negeri, Indrasari Wisnu Wardhana, dan tiga bos perusahaan minyak swasta ditetapkan sebagai tersangka kasus dugaan tindakan melawan hukum atas pemberian izin ekspor minyak goreng, pemerintah bereaksi.||||Presiden melarang ekspor sawit dan minyak goreng, mulai 28 April 2022, agar stok minyak goreng di dalam negeri melimpah, dengan harapan harganya perlahan turun.||||Namun, menanggapi larangan ini, Gabungan Pengusaha Kelapa Sawit Indonesia, atau GAPKI, meminta pemerintah untuk mengevaluasi kebijakan ini.||||Baca Juga Soroti Kasus Korupsi Minyak Goreng, AHY: Usut Tuntas, Jangan Sampai Ada Kambing Hitam! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282891/soroti-kasus-korupsi-minyak-goreng-ahy-usut-tuntas-jangan-sampai-ada-kambing-hitam||||Komisi Pengawas Persaingan Usaha, KPPU, sebelumnya telah mengendus indikasi praktik kartel, di antara para pengusaha minyak goreng.||||Namun, struktur pasar oligopoli yang tak sehat, seakan membuat pemerintah tak punya pilihan.||||Organisasi Kelompok Sawit Watch menilai, kebijakan presiden melarang ekspor minyak sawit mentah, dan minyak goreng, tak bisa serta merta menurunkan harga.||||Masalah utama justru berada di kebijakan pemerintah, yang tak kunjung membenahi struktur pasar minyak goreng, yang tak sehat.||||Tak hanya bisa diakali dengan perubahan strategi produksi oleh para produsen, kebijakan larangan ekspor minyak goreng, juga dikhawatirkan, bisa memicu kebijakan balasan dari luar negeri, yang bergantung pada pasokan minyak sawit mentah Indonesia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282923/kebijakan-presiden-larang-ekspor-minyak-disebut-tak-akan-turunkan-harga-minyak-goreng

title: Jalur Pantura Semakin Padat Pemudik! Arteri Karawang hingga Cirebon Didominasi Kendaraan Roda Empat
description: KOMPAS.TV - Arus mudik di Jalur Pantura Jawa semakin padat.||||Sabtu (23/4) malam, Jalur Arteri Karawang menuju Pantura Cirebon maupun Jawa Tengah dipadati kendaraan pemudik yang memilih perjalanan malam.||||Pemudik roda dua maupun roda empat mulai memadati Jalur Arteri Karawang menuju Cirebon, Jawa Tengah hingga Jawa Timur.||||Perjalanan malam banyak dipilih pemudik untuk perjalanan pulang kampung karena pertimbangan cuaca yang lebih sejuk dan perjalanan cenderung lebih lancar dibandingkan pada siang hari.||||Berdasarkan pantauan Kompas TV, gelombang arus mudik mengalami peningkatan sejak Jumat (22/4) malam dan terus terjadi hingga Sabtu (23/4) malam.||||Meski demikian, arus lalu lintas masih terpantau lancar.||||Sementara itu, peningkatan arus kendaraan pemudik juga terlihat di Gerbang Tol Palimanan, Cirebon, Jawa Barat, pada Sabtu (23/4) malam.||||Kendaraan berpelat luar daerah tampak ramai bergerak dari arah Jakarta menuju Jawa Tengah dan Jawa Timur.||||Sebagian kendaraan bahkan memenuhi bagian atap mobil dengan barang-barang untuk dibawa ke kampung halaman.||||Pihak pengelola tol mencoba meniadakan transaksi pembayaran di Gerbang Tol Palimanan untuk memperlancar laju kendaraan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282862/jalur-pantura-semakin-padat-pemudik-arteri-karawang-hingga-cirebon-didominasi-kendaraan-roda-empat

title: RARA MUTTON CURRY | RARA GOSHT | MUTTON RARA | MUTTON RARA GOSHT
description: Rara Mutton Curry | Rara Gosht | Mutton Rara Recipe | Mutton Rara Gosht | How To Make Rara Mutton | Keema Mutton Masala | Rara Mutton | Rara Mutton Recipe | Mutton Rara | Mutton curry | Rara Mutton Bhuna | Spice Eats Mutton Rara |Ingredients for Rare Mutton Curry:|(Tsp- Teaspoon; Tbsp- Tablespoon )| |- Mutton Ribs & Chops - 500 gms|- Muton Mince (Keema) - 250 gms.|For marinating the 500 gms ribs & chops: |- Turmeric Powder- 1/2 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 2 tsp|- Coriander Powder- 2 tsp|- Salt- 1 tsp |- Ginger Garlic paste- 1.5 tsp|- Curd- 5-6 tbsp|Tempering:|- Green Cardamom- 6|- Cinnamon -4 |- Cloves- 6|- Black Cardamom- 2|- Black Peppercorns-6-8|- Mace(Javitri)- few petals|Spice Powders:|- Turmeric- 1/2 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 2 tsp|- Red Chilli Powder- 1 tsp|- Coriander powder- 1.5 tsp|- Garam Masala Powder- 3/4 tsp|- Kasuri Methi Powder-1/2 tsp powder|Other ingredients:|- Onions chopped - 300 gms (4 medium)|- Crushed ginger - 1 tbsp|- Crushed garlic- 1 tbsp|- Sliced & roughly crushed green Chillies- 2-3 |- Tomato pur√©e (readymade or fresh) 3 tbsp|- Ghee- 4-5 tbsp|- Oil- 2 tbsp|- Coriander leaves, chopped- 2 tbsp|Preparation:|- Marinate the ribs & chops with the ingredients specified. Mix and set aside for an hour. |- Chop the onions. Peel and roughly crush the ginger and garlic. |- Also slice the green chillies and roughly crush these. Set aside. |- For the tomato pur√©e, you can use readymade tomato pur√©e/paste or blend red tomatoes to give fresh tomato pur√©e. |- Dry roast the Kasuri Methi and then crush it with your hand. Set aside for use later.|- Also chop the coriander leaves and set aside. |Process:|- Heat a mix of ghee & oil in a curry pan and then add the whole spices. |- Give a stir and then add the crushed ginger, garlic and green chillies. Fry for 1 min and then add the chopped onions. Fry on medium heat for 13 mins till the onions are light brown in colour. |- Now add the minced meat and fry on high heat for 2 mins. Add all the Spice Powders other than GMP & Kasuri Methi, give a mix .Also add 3/4 tsp salt. Fry on medium heat for 5 mins till the keema is browned & oil separates. |- Now add the marinated mutton and fry on high to medium high heat for 5 mins. Continue to bhunno (fry) for another 5 mins on medium low heat. Add the readymade tomato pur√©e, give a mix and cook on medium low heat for 2-3 mins. |- Add 300 ml water, give a mix and cover & cook on low heat for around 20 mins. |- Now add the Garam Masala Powder & Kasuri Methi powder. Mix and cover and cook on low heat for 7-8 mins (or 6-7 ???) till the meat is tender and the keema gravy coats the mutton pieces and oil separates. |- Garnish with chopped coriander leaves. Mix and simmer for 1-2 mins. Serve hot with Roti or Rumali Roti. |#raramutton #raragosht #muttonrara #raramuttonrecipe #raramuttoncurry #muttonrararecipe #muttoncurry #spiceeats #spiceeatsrecipes #spiceeatsmutton

title: Petani Protes Larangan Ekspor Minyak Goreng: Sawit Bukan Hanya Milik Oligarki, Tapi Juga Petani
description: Presiden Joko Widodo memutuskan untuk melarang ekspor minyak goreng dan bahan bakunya, mulai 28 april nanti. Pelarangan itu dilakukan agar pasokan minyak goreng di dalam negeri kembali melimpah dan harganya murah. Namun, harga murah belum didapat, alih-alih kebijakan pukul rata itu justru menuai kritik dari sebagian kalangan, yang mempertanyakan nasib lebih dari 30 juta ton crude palm oil akan dikemanakan. Sementara kebutuhan dalam negeri hanya 6-7 juta ton. Lantas efektifkah kebijakan pelarangan ekspor Jokowi ini?|Kebijakan pukul rata larangan ekspor minyak goreng dan bahan bakunya menuai kritik. Sebagian kalangan mempertanyakan nasib lebih dari 30 juta ton produksi crude palm oil akan dikemanakan. Sementara kebutuhan dalam negeri hanya 6-7 juta ton. Lantas efektifkah kebijakan pelarangan ekspor Jokowi untuk mengatasi persoalan kelangkaan dan tingginya harga minyak goreng?|Eva Yunizar membahasnya dalam dialog wawancara via zoom bersama Andre Rosiade selaku Anggota Komisi VI DPR RI F-Partai Gerindra, Bhima Yudhistira selaku Direktur CELIOS dan Petani Sawit, Wayan Supadno.

title: Global National: April 23, 2022 | Mixed messages emerge from front lines in Ukraine
description: Ukrainian President Zelenskyy spoke in person to hundreds of journalists in an underground train station in Kyiv. The president answered questions for more than an hour as Russia continued to pound the front lines. And as western leaders try to re-start negotiations, mixed messages from the front lines are emerging. Mike Drolet has more.| |An early and furious start to the U.S. wildfire season: At least 11 million Americans are under a red flag warning to be extremely careful as fast-moving fires sweep through Arizona, New Mexico and Colorado. Evacuation orders have been issued for several counties as firefighters battle flames fueled by extreme winds. Jennifer Johnson has the latest.| |The Conservative leadership race hit a key benchmark this week. At least eight candidates made the deadline to file the paperwork and submit the first installment of the $300,000 entry fee they need to pay by the end of the month in order to stay in the race. On the West Block, David Akin is joined by two leading lights in Canada‚Äôs Conservative movement, former Saskatchewan premier Brad Wall and former cabinet minister James Moore to examine the health of this race - and the health of the party. | |A battle is brewing in Quebec over a proposed language law that could force college students to take three core courses in French. Anglophone groups say Bill 96 would make many students fail and potentially drive many out of the province. Dan Spector looks at the growing push-back as the legislation nears adoption. | |The job market in Canada is red-hot right now and it‚Äôs causing a power shift. There are about a million openings across the country and just about the same number of people looking for jobs. Companies are now being forced to offer more than just a paycheque to attract workers. Anne Gaviola has more. | |Alberta is leading the world in a program that gets surgery patients back on their feet faster. Along with reducing hospitalization time, experts say the program could also cut costs and pain medication use for patients. Su-Ling-Goh reports.| |A thrift store in British Columbia is making a name for itself. Not necessarily for what it sells, but how it‚Äôs helping the community it relies on. In just four years the owner of Danny‚Äôs Dynamite Deals has donated tens of thousands of dollars to local schools and charities. title: Xander Schauffele & Patrick Cantlay shoot 12-under 60 | Round 3 | Zurich Classic | 2022

title: Why There's No Red iPhone 13 Pro
description: Apple is known for their world class industrial design. So when they decide to use color in a product, they tend to do it well. And nowhere is this more evident than on the iPhone. The gold 5s, rose gold 6s, and midnight green 11 started new design trends that rippled through the tech industry. But one color in particular has stuck around; Product Red. It debuted with the second generation iPod nano in 2006. And has been used on several iPhone models since then. But mysteriously, the color has never been used on a pro model. And the reason comes down to marketing.

title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Manchester United (3-1) | Premier League | Tavares, Saka, Xhaka-boom!
description: We moved back into the top four thanks to a pulsating victory over Manchester United.|It was a highly charged, incident-packed encounter from start to finish. Nuno Tavares and Bukayo Saka fired us into a two-goal lead inside half an hour, before United rallied to halve the deficit through Cristiano Ronaldo.|Bruno Fernandes then missed a penalty before Granit Xhaka sealed the points with a superb 25-yard drive. |These lunchtime kick offs can often have a sedate atmosphere early on. Not this one. The crowd were up for it from the kick off, and the team responded immediately.|There were just two minutes on the clock when Tavares gave us the lead. Xhaka‚Äôs deep cross was missed by everyone in the United defence and found its way though to Saka. His shot was parried by David de Gea but Tavares was in the right place at the far post to tuck home.|It was the full back‚Äôs first goal for the club since joining from Benfica last summer.|United came back. Anthony Elanga had a low shot well saved by Aaron Ramsdale before Gabriel put in a great block after Ramsdale had presented the ball to Fernandes.|Diogo Dalot was next to go close for the visitors, curling a shot from 20 yards over the keeper and against the crossbar.|Chances were coming at both ends, and Eddie Nketiah had a great chance after being slid through on goal by Martin Odegaard but his shot was straight at de Gea.|Moments later Nketiah thought he had beaten the keeper, only for the goal to be ruled out by VAR for a very close offside call. However there was a foul on Saka in the build up, and a spot kick was awarded instead.|For the second time in a week the England man stepped up and netted from the penalty spot.|The two-goal advantage didn‚Äôt last long. United had been a threat throughout the opening half hour, and pulled a goal back through Cristiano Ronaldo, who stole in at the far post to fire home a looping cross. Ramsdale‚Äôs moment of hesitation proved costly.|The first half was action-packed, and had flown by. Odegaard had another shot tipped away in injury-time ‚Äì one of six attempts on target in the opening 45 minutes for us.|Tavares should have hit the target soon after the interval. He found space inside the box, beat his man superbly, but blazed a shot high and wide.|Tavares‚Äôs eventful afternoon continued when he gave away a penalty for handball. Fernandes stepped up, but his shot hit the post and went behind for a goal kick.|It was a big let off, and moments later there was another when Ronaldo‚Äôs goal was ruled out for offside by the barest of margins.|Ramsdale came up with a huge save at his near post to turn Dalot‚Äôs shot onto the woodwork.|We were living dangerously, but Granit Xhaka‚Äôs fierce drive relieved the pressure.|He picked up the ball five yards outside the box, shifted it on to his trusty left foot, and arrowed his shot beyond the despairing de Gea just inside the post.|The Emirates erupted. With the two-goal cushion restored, we closed out the game to earn a second big win in the space of four days.|Teams: |Arsenal: Ramsdale, Cedric, White, Gabriel, Tavares; Elneny, Xhaka;, Saka, Odegaard, Smith Rowe,  Nketiah.|Substitutes: Leno, Tomiyasu, Holding, Lokonga, Azeez, Swanson, Pepe, Martinelli, Lacazette|Manchester United: De Gea, Dalot, Lindelof, Varane, Alex Telles,  McTominay, Matic,  Elanga, Fernandes, Sancho, Ronaldo.|Substitutes  Henderson, Wan-Bissaka, Bailly, Jones, Maguire, Mata, Lingard, Rashford, Garnacho.|#arsenal #bukayosaka #granitxhaka |It puts us six points ahead of United, with five games remaining.Enjoy match highlights, training and behind the scenes to get closer to the likes of Bukayo Saka, Emile Smith Rowe, Vivianne Miedema, Nicolas Pepe, Alexandre Lacazette, Leah Williamson, Bernd Leno, Nikita Parris, Tobin Heath, Mana Iwabuchi, Jordan Nobbs, Takehiro Tomiyasu, Kim Little, Gabriel Martinelli, Aaron Ramsdale, Beth Mead, Ben White, Thomas Partey and more.|Subscribe to the Official Arsenal YouTube Channel: https://arsn.al/youtube|Follow us on Facebook: https://arsn.al/facebook|Follow us on Twitter: https://arsn.al/twitter|Follow us on Instagram: https://arsn.al/instagram|Follow us on TikTok: https://arsn.al/tiktok|This is the Official YouTube channel for Arsenal Football Club.|For more match action, highlights and training videos, make sure you become a digital member and sign up to Arsenal Player. It's FREE and is the Home of the Game: https://arsn.al/arsenalplayer|Arsenal Football Club were formed in 1886 and amassed 13 League titles, 14 FA Cups. Some of their greatest players include: Thierry Henry, Dennis Bergkamp, Tony Adams, Ian Wright, Robert Pires, Liam Brady, Patrick Vieira, Cliff Bastin and Charlie George.

title: Penggeledahan 10 Lokasi Dugaan Korupsi Minyak Goreng, Kejaksaan Agung Sita 650 Dokumen
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Kejaksaan Agung menggeledah 10 lokasi dalam kasus dugaan korupsi dalam pemberian izin fasilitas ekspor minyak sawit mentah, atau CPO.||||Dari sepuluh lokasi, penggeledahan salah satunya dilakukan di rumah Dirjen Perdagangan Luar Negeri Kementerian Perdagangan, Indrasari Wisnu Wardhana yang telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka.||||Baca Juga Kejagung Ungkap Peran Dirjen Kemendag Soal Korupsi Minyak Goreng di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282507/kejagung-ungkap-peran-dirjen-kemendag-soal-korupsi-minyak-goreng||||Penggeledahan dilakukan pada Selasa (05/04) lalu.||||Tak hanya rumah Dirjen Kemendag, Kejaksaan Agung juga menggeledah kantor Kementerian Perdagangan di Jakarta.||||Dari penggeledahan, Kejagung menyita 650 dokumen serta barang bukti elektronik.||||Barang bukti elektronik ini kini tengah didalami penyidik, untuk mencari tahu secara rinci percakapan para tersangka sehingga berakibat pada perbuatan melawan hukum.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282829/penggeledahan-10-lokasi-dugaan-korupsi-minyak-goreng-kejaksaan-agung-sita-650-dokumen

title: Josh Pate On Best Teams Over NEXT 5 Years (Late Kick Cut)
description: College Football season is still a few months away, but with spring practices wrapping up and spring games happening all across the country Josh Pate responded to a viewer question on Late Kick Live Ep 254 about which programs are better positioned over the next 5 seasons. With UGA having just beaten Alabama for the national title, would you choose the Tide or the Dawgs for the near future? What about Oklahoma and USC? title: The key to Max's F1 Imola sprint win by Peter Windsor
description: The Saturday sprint F1 race at Imola  looked to be another demonstration of unabashed superiority by Charles Leclerc and Ferrari...until the right-front Pirelli on the F1-75 began to grain and thus to lose grip. Then Max Verstappen, the tyres on his Red Bull RB18 working perfectly, closed in for the kill. In this video, at 06:20, Peter Windsor offers a suggestion as to why there was such a difference in late-race tyre performance between the two cars. Calling on data from FP2 at Imola this morning, Peter also looks ahead to the Emilia Romagna Grand Prix at Imola on Sunday, when the protagonists will also be using harder Pirelli compounds. (Even so, the soft tyre still looks to be very raceable off the line, even with a higher fuel load.)  Peter also analyses another disappointing day for Mercedes; a strong result for McLaren-Mercedes and Alfa Romeo; and the impressive drive by Haas' Mick Schumacher.|With thanks to Jetcraft, the world's largest buyer and seller of executive jets, for their support of this channel|https://jetcraft.com|Follow Peter @peterdwindsor|Images: AMG Mercedes, Red Bull, Alfa Romeo, Scuderia Ferrari, McLaren F1 and Haas|With thanks to Alpinestars|https: alpinestars.com|This channel supports the Race Against Dementia:|https://raceagainstdementia.com|#STANDWITHUKRAINE

title: India breaks Pak's record: 78,000 wave national flag together in Bihar I Watch
description: More than 78,000 Indians simultaneously waved the national flag at the Jagdishpur town in Bihar's Bhojpur district on Saturday, breaking a record that was set by Pakistan 18 years ago when 56,000 Pakistanis waved their national flag at an event in Lahore. The Indian national flag was waved at Jagdishpur for a full five minutes on the occasion of 164th death anniversary of Veer Kunwar Singh, the then king of Jagdishpur who is regarded as one of the heroes of the First War of Independence in 1857. This event was organised as a part of the Union government's 'Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav' initiative. title: Ukraine war update: How is Russia doing & what does Ukraine need? | DW News
description: US satellite images appear to show another mass grave in a cemetery east of Mariupol. Pictures taken in late March and mid April suggest fresh parallel trenches were dug. Ukraine has accused Russia of trying to hide evidence of war crimes during the assault on the city. Russia denies the claims.|Ukraine's Azov Regiment has released a video of civilians sheltering in bunkers beneath the Azovstal steel plant in Mariupol. It's not clear when or where the video was filmed. Russian president Vladimir Putin ordered his forces not to storm the plant earlier this week but Ukraine says attacks in the area have continued.|United Nations Secretary-General Antonio Guterres is set to visit Moscow on Tuesday to meet Russian President Vladimir Putin. He'll then head to Ukraine for talks with President Volodymyr Zelenskyy. Guterres will discuss steps to bring about peace following Russia's invasion of Ukraine.|Russia has confirmed the death of one of the crew members of its flagship missile cruiser Moskva, a week after it sank in the Black Sea. The Ministry of Defense said nearly 400 crew members were evacuated. Kremlin critics suspect a much higher number of dead and missing, saying the ship's crew was about 500 strong.|A court in Moscow has ordered opposition activist Vladimir Kara-Murza to remain in pre-trial detention. He's accused of spreading fake news about Russia's army after denouncing the war. Kara-Murza has long been a critic of the Kremlin, and has survived two poison attacks. Human rights groups have called for his release.|Ukraine has warned that Russia plans to attack more countries and expand its war. President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said Ukraine's neighbour Moldova should be concerned about Russia's latest military strategy. |Moldova is home to Trans-nistria, which is a breakaway pro-Russian region which borders Ukraine. Russia is in control of Ukraine's south-east regions, seen here in blue. title: J&K: PM Modi to inaugurate Banihal-Qazigund tunnel; How it will boost connectivity
description: PM Modi who will be on J&K visit on Sunday will inaugurate the Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel, built at a cost of over Rs 3,100 crore. The 8.45 km long tunnel would reduce the road distance between Banihal and Qazigund by 16 km, and reduce journey time by around one and a half hour. The tunnel would help establish an all weather connection between Jammu and Kashmir, and bring the two regions closer. On Sunday, all eyes will be on PM Modi who will inaugurating this tunnel. title: Ultimate Bangladeshi Food!! GIANT BEEF MEZBAN in Chittagong, Bangladesh!!
description: üé• Watch - Unique Village Food Bangladesh: https://youtu.be/BMhdzxNR3ps|üáßüá© Huge thanks to @Petuk Couple |üîî SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/MarkWiensSubscribe Don‚Äôt miss new food videos!|CHITTAGONG, BANGLADESH - Welcome to Chittagong in the south of Bangladesh, along the coast, is famous for its mezban - a traditional meal celebration where a full cow is cooked into 4 different dishes. Today we have the extremely special opportunity to see the dishes of a mezban being  prepared and to watch the entire process.|Mezzan Haile Ayun (https://goo.gl/maps/TBKPjdYTHNudh4nL9) is a restaurant in Chittagong with locations in Dhaka and Sharjah that specializes in mezban. We had the privilege to go to their central kitchen to watch the entire process. Every mezban meal starts with an entire cow - the full cow. The meat must be fresh and they parted it out within 45 minutes, all the way from cow to cubes.|The most important dish is the mezbani beef, a curry, but like a slow cooked stew filled with beef, a huge amount of spices, green chilies, mustard oil, and one of the signature tastes from a spice called radhuni. Every dish cooks over fire, slow cooked until fully mingled and flavors melting together. Additionally there‚Äôs black beef cooked in spices and dry fried until all the spices were caked onto each cube meat. Another dish is the daal, which is cooked with all the organs of the cow. And finally the bones which are cooked for the flavor, bone marrow, in a soup. The entire meal, all four dishes are a traditional Bangladeshi mezban.|The meal was outstanding, so much flavor so fresh, and so complex. All the dishes each went together in perfect harmony. It‚Äôs one of the best food experiences in Bangladesh and it was truly memorable.|Thank you so much to Petuk Couple (https://www.youtube.com/c/PetukCouple) for arranging this and for showing me around Bangladesh!|üìçMezzan Haile Ayun: https://goo.gl/maps/TBKPjdYTHNudh4nL9|üéµMUSIC: |https://goo.gl/HwVjdo|‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî|üëïGet t-shirts and caps:|https://migrationology.com/store/|‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî|üì±FOLLOW:|Instagram: https://instagram.com/migrationology|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/migrationology
